Create server image:
while in /register directory
docker build -t servername .

Running server:
docker run -p5000:5000 servername

Running client image:
while in /client directory
docker build -t clientname .

Running client:
docker run -p8080:80 clientname


Verification:
Name and Surname - first letter must be BIG
Login - 3 to 12 small letters long
Password - at least 8 letters long